articles.title: Five Fun Facts
articles.contents:
I’m originally from San Francisco, Ca.



Figure 1: Darwin at the Golden Gate Bridge



I do aerial arts (like you can see in cirque du soleil!). I can do
silks, trapeze, and hoop/lyra, but my favorite is lyra.



Figure 2: Lyra







Figure 3: Silks



I love to bake, especially chocolate chip cookies.
I have a dog named Darwin after Charles Darwin (in the first
pic!).
I love being outside and active. On the weekends I’m usually
hiking, camping or exploring Baltimore!




Figure 4: Arches National Park
